               <head>Commentary on Jeremiah by Japheth ben Ali ha-Levi</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>The commentary of Japheth ben Ali ha-Levi on the book of Jeremiah.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="jrb-Hebr">Hebrew, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="252v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush Yirme῾yahu</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">פרוש ירמיהו </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Contains Jeremiah 14:19-22, 15:9-10, 26:1-52:16.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The pointed Hebrew biblical text of Jeremiah 14:19-22, 15:9-10, 26:1-16, 20, 26:24-28:1, 28:12-29:9, 29:19-30:17, 30:22-31:4, 31:8, 22, 31:23-32:9, 32:32-33:11, 33:14-34:1, 34:8-35:7, 35:12-37:12, 37:15-38:13, 38:22-39:5, 39:9-44:13, 44:16-21, 26-30, 45:4-50:2, 50:4-18, 50:21-52:18, accompanied by a verse by verse Arabic translation, is embodied.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A number of masoretic notes, some of them added by a later hand.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Several notes by various later hands are added in the margins.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/54984961">Japheth ben Ali, ha-Levi</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/54984961">יפת בן עלי, הלוי</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <listBibl>
                        
                        
                        
